Module hu.unipannon.virt.plot
Package hu.unipannon.virt.plot.frame.vertical

Class VerticalAxis

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent
        • javafx.scene.Group
          • hu.unipannon.virt.plot.frame.Container
            • hu.unipannon.virt.plot.frame.vertical.VerticalAxis
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
    public class VerticalAxis
extends Container
    Base class of the Vertical Axis, it contains all the components in the axis. In order to turn on items, the Axis object must be turned on too. The class extends the Container class, it is usually bound to the Frame class.
    Author:
    Tóth Bálint

      • setDivisors

        public void setDivisors​(double[] divisors,
                        java.lang.String[] labels)
        Sets the divisor points and labels of the axis. Divisor points must be normalized in the [0;1] interval. The two arrays must be of same length.
        Parameters:
        divisors - divisor points for the axis.
        labels - labels for the points.
